Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ We ♪\N♪ Are the crystal ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:06.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Gems ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.40,0:00:08.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ We'll always save the day ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.67,0:00:11.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Steven: ♪ And if you think\Nwe can't, we'll ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.01,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Always find a way ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:15.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ That's why the people ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:18.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Of this world ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Believe in ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.75,0:00:20.55,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Garnet ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:21.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Amethyst: ♪ Amethyst ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.62,0:00:23.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,Pearl: ♪ And Pearl ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,And Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.79,0:00:31.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,红宝石们回来了?\NThe rubies are back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:33.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们开着那个小飞船来的\NThey showed up on their little ship
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:34.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看起来很生气\Nacting very angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:35.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我让她们“中场休息”一下\Nso I put them in time-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.83,0:00:38.37,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以为这件事已经解决了\NI thought we were done with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们回来干嘛\NWhy did you come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:43.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,放出来一个问问她们要干什么吧\NLet's release one and just ask what they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.41,0:00:45.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!哦!能让我来选吗?\NOoh! Ooh!Can I pick?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.14,0:00:46.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,选吧\NGo for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.04,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦!就选腿腿吧!\NOh!Let's talk to Leggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.41,0:00:51.68,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,腿腿?\NLeggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我根据她们宝石的位置分别起了名字\NI named them based on the placement of their gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:59.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们是腿腿,膀子,脐脐,眼宝和,额,万事通\NThere's Leggy, Army, Navy,Eyeball, and, uh...Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.82,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,腿腿看上去最好说话\NLeggy seems like the easiest to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.82,0:01:04.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,腿腿,下来吧!\NLeggy, come on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.63,0:01:08.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿!嗨,我叫史蒂文\NHey! Hi.I'm Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.36,0:01:10.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们回来地球做什么?\NWhat brings you back to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:16.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃...我也不知道?\NUh...I don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:18.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,呃,我懂你\NOh, uh,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以前也经常忘记为什么出任务\NI used to forget why we'd go on missions all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:22.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那我去那边站着好了\NI'll just go stand over here then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.08,0:01:25.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们来试试膀子吧\NLet's take a chance on Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:27.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,下午好!\NGood afternoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:30.55,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我要把你们撕成--\NI'll tear you limb --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.55,0:01:32.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-哈?-嘿,别这样没礼貌\N-Huh?-Hey.Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:35.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啥?!我要把--\NWhy, I ought to --
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.19,0:01:36.39,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗷\NAw.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:39.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-嘿,你干嘛...-下一个!\N-Hey, what the...-Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:40.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃...脐脐?\NUh...Navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:44.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,要是我没记错的话,我们是来地球...\NIf I remember correctly,we were on Earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:47.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃...\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,太尴尬了\NThis is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:50.24,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦吼\NOh-ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦 啊!\NOh. Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.61,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,啊!\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:55.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧 呃,眼宝?\NOkay.Uh, eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:02:00.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我才不会跟你们讲任何东西!\NI'm not telling y'all nothing about nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.42,0:02:04.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,剩下最后一个是...呃,万事通\NThe only one left now is, uh...Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英在哪?!\NWhere's Jasper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:08.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,上次我们来,\NLast time we came,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.22,0:02:11.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你骗我们玩那个蠢游戏!\Nyou tricked us into playing that stupid game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后你又说,“她在海王星呢”\NThen, you said,"She's on Neptune,"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.26,0:02:16.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我们又去找,她根本不在那!\Nso we looked,and she wasn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.70,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她没在海王星\NShe wasn't on Neptune
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:23.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,也没在这蠢太阳系的任何一颗行星上!\Nor any other planet in this whole dang solar system!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.67,0:02:26.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,快告诉我们她在哪\NTell us where she is right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.51,0:02:31.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,别玩游戏,别耍伎俩,也别搞伪装\NNo games, no tricks,and no slick disguises.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对!\N-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿!\NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:37.15,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我在这儿呢!\NI'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她搞笑呢?这根本不可能骗--\NIs she serious?There's no way this is gonna --
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看!是铁石英!\NLook! It's Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:48.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英!我是红宝石编号1F4-Cut-4ND.\NJasper!I'm Ruby 1F4-Cut-4ND.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:50.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,曾经参与过地球战役\NI fought in the war for Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃...稍息\NUh...at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:57.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我当时在第六区的战场,听到了你的传闻\NI was on the ground in Facet 6 when I heard the tale
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.20,0:02:59.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,说是第九区宝宝基地有个石英很厉害\Nof the Facet 9 Kindergarten Quartz That Could.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:03.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,他们说你戴着头盔从土地中蹦出来\NThey said you popped out of the ground with your helmet on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:06.51,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在日落之前干掉了80个水晶战士\Nand took out 80 crystal gems before the sun went down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当我知道这次任务是为了找你\NWhen I found out this mission was to look for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我差点没控记巨我记己!\NI nearly dissipated my form!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:14.72,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很荣幸终于见到你\NIt is an honor to finally meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,那就是我!\NYup. That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:19.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一直这么大个儿,从来没小过--\NAlways huge, never small,all the --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:23.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,自打出生之日起!\Nall the time since I was made!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:25.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,等下\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.53,0:03:28.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你看起来和我想象中不一样啊\NYou look different than I thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:30.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,露馅了吧\NOh, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.00,0:03:35.11,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,我晒黑了一点,你造,太阳晒的嘛\NOh, you must mean my tan --you know, from the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的地球太阳!啊!\NStupid Earth sun!Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.18,0:03:40.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我恨这颗星球!\NI hate this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.45,0:03:42.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,诅咒这颗星球!\NCurse this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不管怎样,还好最后找到了你\NWell, it's a good thing we finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.85,0:03:51.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,黄钻在等着你回去\NYellow Diamond is awaiting your return.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们现在马上带你回母星\NWe'll take you back to Homeworld right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.30,0:03:55.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不行!我是说--\NNo! I mean --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我,铁石英\NI, Jasper,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,已经决定呆在地球了\Nhave decided to stay on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:01.67,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-啥?!-为啥!\N-What?!-Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对啊,为什么,铁石英?\NYeah, why, Jasper?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:06.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,因为我要在这里看住这些家伙\NBecause I gotta stay here with these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.98,0:04:11.58,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,必须把她们关起来...为钻石们效力\NYep, gotta keep 'em prisoner... for the diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.68,0:04:16.82,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-铁石英-多么伟大的牺牲\N-Jasper.-Such devotion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:20.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧,黄钻肯定想知道这些事\NWell, Yellow will definitely want to know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.42,0:04:23.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你需要在最近的钻石基地做报告\NYou'll have to file a report at the nearest Diamond base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:24.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,钻石基地在哪?\NWhere's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.34,0:04:25.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,路上是不是有经过?\Npassed it on our way here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.75,0:04:28.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们几个呆瓜!是在,呃...\NYou dummies!It's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:29.16,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,是--嗯\NIt's -- Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:31.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在那儿呢!\NIt's there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:35.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我要一路保持这个形态到月球?\NI gotta hold this all the way to the moon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:37.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,我是说押持\NUh, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.53,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,押持这些...犯人\NHold these...prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,如果去月球的话得把这些叛军犯人带着\NGotta bring the rebel prisoners if we're going to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:46.38,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不能把她们放在这里没人看管\NCan't leave them here unsupervised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:48.78,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,很好 上飞船!\NVery well.To the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.50,0:04:52.32,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你在搞什么?这根本成功不了\NWhat are you doing?This isn't going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你不能一直保持这个形态啊\NYou can't hold that form forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.56,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我能做到的\NI can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:57.59,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们先去月球,再回来\NWe'll go to the moon,come back,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:04:59.33,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后她们走就是了\Nand they'll leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,跟我一起演就行\NJust play along.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.03,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,嘿!\NOh, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们几个也要当犯人吗?\NYou guys want to be prisoners, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:05.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不要\NNot really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:07.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好吧,就问问\NAll right.Just checking.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇,这里面好大!\NWhoa.It's huge in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.94,0:05:14.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我以为会超级挤的\NI thought it'd be super-cramped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:17.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿!这可不是去郊游!\NHey!This ain't no pleasure cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:19.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,说得对!\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:24.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,放尊重点,水-水货战士们!\NShow some respect,you crystal germs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:25.22,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对,教训下她们,铁石英!\NYeah,you tell 'em, Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,地球上那么多水可不是水货嘛!\NI bet they got those germs from Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:28.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗷,真倒霉!\NAw, curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.89,0:05:30.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不敢相信我们竟然被抓了!\NI can't believe we've been caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还是被铁石英抓到的!\NAnd by none other than Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.23,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,真是气死我惹\NI'm so cross over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:35.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对啊\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:38.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,都怪铁石英--就是她抓的我们\NThat sure is Jasper --the one that caught us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:39.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,气死惹\NHarumph.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.93,0:05:42.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,多么一种耻辱啊!\NOf all the indignities!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:46.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,千刀万剐随你,我自闭口不言\NDo what you want.I'll never talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.91,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我倒希望你能闭嘴呢\NHuh, I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.91,0:05:51.54,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对啊,哈哈,她话真多\NYeah.She talks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.55,0:05:53.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,快去那边坐着!\NGo sit over there now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:56.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇哦,铁石英又强壮又风趣\NWow!Jasper's so funny and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.49,0:05:58.55,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我也这么想呢!\NI was just thinking that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:00.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这太有趣了!\NThis is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-铁石英!-啊,我是铁石英!\N-Jasper!-Agh! I'm Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:05.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,请你坐上我的位置,就在最前--\NPlease feel free to take my seat right up front --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:06.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那个船长座位\Nthe captain's seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:08.46,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这是我的荣幸\NIt would be an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.46,0:06:09.66,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.66,0:06:11.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好,没问题\NYes.Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,希望你觉得座位舒服\NI hope it's to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还行吧\NIt's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.17,0:06:16.10,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你可以随时\NYou can go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,驾驶飞船飞向月球基地\Nand head towards the moon base whenever you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:19.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,但...\NBuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:21.87,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,当然可以!呵\NOf course!Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.44,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嗯\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:25.18,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃\NUh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.55,0:06:30.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,听着\NUh, listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:33.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我是铁石英,我因为刚刚\NI'm Jasper,and I'm too worn out
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.09,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,抓她们叛军上飞船所以很累\Nfrom catching rebels to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,所以我就坐这儿,像这样\Nso I'll just sit here,like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后你驾驶飞船带我们上月球\Nand you work the thing to get us to the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:40.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,明白没?\NGot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.30,0:06:42.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,明白,当然的\NYes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.40,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那么,去月球?\NTo the moon, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:46.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对的,去月球!\NTo the moon, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,对的,去月球!\NTo the moon, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:55.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们即将到达月球\NWe'll be arriving shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:57.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,把座位捂热了\NHey, keep my seat warm
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我去看看那些,呃,犯人们\Nwhile I check on our,uh, prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:02.52,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好的,铁石英,好主意\NYes, Jasper.Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不!\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,离我们远点,你个莽夫!\NStay away from us,you brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.29,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,低调点,珍珠\NTone it down, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:12.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那个红宝石都想把你丢出太空去了\NThat one ruby wants to throw you out into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.13,0:07:16.63,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,抱歉,太入戏了\NSorry.Got a bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:18.83,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,呃,你还好吗,紫晶?\NUh, you okay, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:20.93,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你已经保持这种形态超长时间了\NYou've been holding that form forever now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.60,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我能控制住\NI've got it under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.80,0:07:27.14,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿!我回去的时候那个座位最好还是热着的!\NHey, my seat better still be warm when I get over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:40.99,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,警报解除!\NAll clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.79,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这边请,铁石英\NRight this way,Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.79,0:07:49.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,铁石英,放过我们可好?\NOh, Jasper,won't you ever let us go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:53.30,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看看这个地方--冻结在过去的状态\NLook at this place --frozen in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.30,0:07:55.07,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,第一纪元时代的基地\NAn era-one base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她的第一纪元基地\N{\i1}Her{\i} era-one base.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.27,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,真是悲剧,发生在她身上那些事\NIt was a tragedy,what happened to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.28,0:08:01.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那到底是谁啊?\NWho is that anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你昨天才出生的吗?!\NWere you made\Nyesterday?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.35,0:08:07.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,那是粉钻\NThat is Pink Diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:11.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,铁石英,最好你来解释\NJasper, maybe it's best if you explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.95,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我来?不要\NWhat, me? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.35,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不,你来\NNo, you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:17.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我,这个,太触动我的情感了\NI'm, like,too messed up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.43,0:08:19.26,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我懂你\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:22.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她是你原本的钻石\NShe was your original diamond.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.50,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,地球是粉钻的殖民地\NEarth was Pink Diamond's colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:27.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,一开始一切都进展顺利\NEverything was going smoothly at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.89,0:08:30.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,宝宝基地在孕育第一批士兵\NKindergartens were incubating their first soldiers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:34.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,大块,温润的石英--就像这个大个子一样--\Nbig, warm pieces of quartz --like this mountain over here --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:39.28,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,在这土地丰富的矿物质中被成功制造出来\Nwere being created from its rich minerals with great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.28,0:08:40.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,突然--砰!\NThen -- bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,粉钻下属的石英战士之一\NOne of Pink Diamond's very own quartz soldiers
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.45,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,发动了叛变然后一发不可收拾\Nstarted a rebellion and took it too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:48.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,叛变发生时你在哪里?\NWhere were you when it happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:51.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哦,你造的,就在附近\NOh, you know, around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.49,0:08:56.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我当时在场 我亲眼看到了\NI was there.I saw it with my own eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.77,0:08:58.86,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我看到水晶战士的头领\NI watched the leader of the crystal gems --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:02.97,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,玫瑰石英--粉碎了粉钻!\NRose Quartz --shatter Pink Diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.81,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.31,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,玫瑰石英才不会那么做!\NRose Quartz would never do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.31,0:09:14.48,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,还-还有,确实,她是要打仗但是--\NA-And, sure,she had to fight but --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:17.05,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她不会粉碎任何人的!\Nbut she would never shatter someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:23.36,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿!遇到问题了\NHey!We got a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.89,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,控制台坏掉了 通讯器也不见了\NThe panel is broken.The communicator is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.89,0:09:29.80,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,这个中心没办法联系黄钻了\NThere's no way to contact Yellow Diamond from this hub.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.80,0:09:31.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-是水晶战士!-难以置信!\N-Crystal gems!-Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-粗鲁!-没教养!\N-Rude!-No respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.65,0:09:34.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,看到了吧!\N-See!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.00,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,她们什么事都做得出来!\NThey'll stoop to anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:37.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们得把你带回母星了\NWe'll have to take you to Homeworld
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:38.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你得亲自做报告\Nto file a report in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不能!\NI can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.78,0:09:42.17,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我不能走!\NI can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.18,0:09:43.75,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-哈?-我没明白\NHuh?-I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.75,0:09:45.71,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-你什么意思?-发生啥事?\N-What do you mean?-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.71,0:09:47.65,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你猜怎么?\NYou know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.65,0:09:48.98,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你懂我的\NYou know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.02,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,帮我个忙,回去母星\NDo me a favor and go back home
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.92,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,然后替我做这个报告\Nand file the report for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.19,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我相信你的,士兵\NI'm trusting you,soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:56.76,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,哇哦\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.76,0:09:58.12,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,没问题!\NOf course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.13,0:09:59.43,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,就这么决定了\NThat settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.43,0:10:01.96,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,好了,红宝石们,返回飞船!\NAll right, rubies,back to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.17,0:10:09.73,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,真棒,紫晶!\N-All right, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:10.88,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你真的坚持住了\NYou really held it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.88,0:10:11.62,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你做到了\NYou did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:15.41,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-我就说你行的-嗷-\N-I told you you could.-Aw.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.00,0:10:25.64,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,需要把你们捎回地球吗?\NHey, you need a ride back to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.64,0:10:27.90,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,如果你想我还可以坐在你腿上,呃--\NI could sit on your lap if you want, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:28.94,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,什么?!\NWhat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:30.84,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我还是铁石英!\NI'm still Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.84,0:10:33.21,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我们又被骗了?!\NWe've been tricked again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:34.74,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,难以置信!\NNo way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.75,0:10:36.08,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,红宝石们,组合!\NRubies, assemble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.29,0:10:48.69,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你们再也别想耍我们了!\NWe won't let you trick us again!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.49,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,嘿,红宝石们!\NHey, rubies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:54.06,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,要打出去打!\NIf you're gonna fight,take it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:11:00.20,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,你不可能这么轻易摆脱我们的!\NYou can't get rid of us that easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.77,0:11:04.34,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,我想她可以\NI bet{\i1} she{\i} can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:13.42,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,-史蒂文!\N-Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:20.77,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ I could even learn\Nhow to love like you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.34,0:11:28.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,♪ Love like you ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.57,720p raw eng,,0,0,0,,
